      <title>降息 50 个基点后套利交易将进一步减少：Yardeni</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-09/carry-trade-to-unwind-further-on-a-50-bps-cut-yardeni-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Yardeni Research 总裁 Ed Yardeni 表示，债券收益率“已经非常接近底部”，并且预计较低的利率将在年底前带来股市上涨的势头。]]></description>
